#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Como xogar"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Obxectivo:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Put the ball into the hole with the least possible hits."
msgstr "Acertar coa bóla no furado co mínimo de tacadas posíbel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname;'s game-play is simple. It is the easiest to learn how to play "
#| "hands-on, and thus a tutorial course is included to guide you through the "
#| "basics. This chapter will guide you through this tutorial. To start the "
#| "tutorial, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Tutorial</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgid ""
"&kolf;'s game-play is simple. It is the easiest to learn how to play hands-"
"on, and thus a tutorial course is included to guide you through the basics. "
"This chapter will guide you through this tutorial. To start the tutorial, "
"choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Tutorial</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"O modo de xogo de &kappname; é simple. É máis fácil de aprender como xogar "
"coas mans na masa e por iso ven incluído un campo de titorial paraguiar "
"polas nocións básicas. Este capítulo conduce a través deste titorial. Para "
"dar inicio a este tutorial, escolle a opción <menuchoice><guimenu>Axuda</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Titorial</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hitting the Ball"
msgstr "Acertar na bóla"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To aim the ball, either line up the mouse behind the ball so the putter "
#| "aims in the direction you want to hit it or press one of the <keycap>Left "
#| "Arrow</keycap> (counterclockwise) or <keycap>Right Arrow</keycap> "
#| "(clockwise) keys, to rotate the putter."
msgid ""
"To aim the ball, either line up the mouse behind the ball so the putter aims "
"in the direction you want to hit it or press one of the &Left; arrow "
"(counterclockwise) or &Right; arrow (clockwise) keys, to rotate the putter."
msgstr ""
"Para apuntar a bóla, pódese tanto aliñar o rato por tras da bóla para que o "
"taco aponte na dirección en que se queira acertar na bóla ou premer unha das "
"teclas <keycap>Esquerda</keycap> (no sentido contrario ao das agullas do "
"reloxo) ou <keycap>Dereita</keycap> (no sentido das agullas do reloxo), para "
"rotar o pau."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To rotate the putter more quickly with the keyboard, hold down &Shift; while "
"pressing or holding the arrow keys. To rotate more slowly, hold down &Ctrl;."
msgstr ""
"Para rotar o pau máis de presa co teclado, mantén premida a tecla &Shift; "
"mentres premes ou mantés premidas as teclas dos cursores. Para rotar máis "
"devagar, mantén premida a tecla &Ctrl;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To hit the ball, press and hold either the &LMB; or <keycap>Down Arrow</"
#| "keycap> key. The longer you hold down the key or button, the more "
#| "strength the putt will have. It will take practice to get a good feel for "
#| "speed."
msgid ""
"To hit the ball, press and hold either the &LMB; or &Down; arrow key. The "
"longer you hold down the key or button, the more strength the putt will "
"have. It will take practice to get a good feel for speed."
msgstr ""
"Para acertar na bóla, preme e mantén premido o &LMB; ou a tecla de cursor "
"<keycap>Abaixo</keycap>. Canto máis tempo mantiveres premida a tecla ou o "
"botón, pero forza terá a tacada. Require práctica ter unha boa noción da "
"velocidade."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To stop the putt while you are still holding moving the putter back in your "
"stroke, press &Esc;."
msgstr ""
"Para interromper a tacada mentres aínda mantés o pau en tensión, preme &Esc;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hit the ball into the hole to move on to the next."
msgstr "Acerta coa bóla no furado para pasar para ao seguinte."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:90 index.docbook:682
#, no-c-format
msgid "Slopes"
msgstr "Ramplas"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Slopes are slanted areas of the course that the golf ball rolls down in "
#| "an expected manner. The light of the golf course is from the upper-left, "
#| "so the brightest slopes will push the ball towards the upper-left corner "
#| "of the hole. Choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show "
#| "Info</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to see an arrow that points in the "
#| "direction the slope will roll the ball."
msgid ""
"Slopes are slanted areas of the course that the golf ball rolls down in an "
"expected manner. The light of the golf course is from the upper-left, so the "
"brightest slopes will push the ball towards the upper-left corner of the "
"hole. Choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Info</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item to see an arrow that points in the "
"direction the slope will roll the ball."
msgstr ""
"As ramplas son áreas inclinadas nas que a bóla rola dunha forma esperada. A "
"luz do campo de golf ven do canto superior esquerdo, de modo que as ramplas "
"máis brillantes empurran a bóla para o canto superior esquerdo do furado. "
"Escolle a opción <menuchoice><guimenu>Furado</guimenu><guimenuitem>Mostrar "
"información</guimenuitem></menuchoice> para ver unha frecha que apunta na "
"dirección na que a rampla fará rodar a bóla."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this tutorial hole, hit the ball onto the upward-pointing slope and let "
"it roll into the cup to move onto the next hole."
msgstr ""
"Neste furado de tutorial, acerte na bóla para que vaia para a rampla que "
"apunta para arriba, e deixe que rebole para a cova, de modo a que pase para "
"o próximo furado."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Directions"
msgstr "Direccións"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "On the next hole, experiment with the other kinds of slopes. There are "
#| "elliptical, vertical, horizontal, and diagonal slopes in &kappname;. Hit "
#| "the ball into the hole."
msgid ""
"On the next hole, experiment with the other kinds of slopes. There are "
"elliptical, vertical, horizontal, and diagonal slopes in &kolf;. Hit the "
"ball into the hole."
msgstr ""
"No próximo furado, experimente cos outros tipos de ramplas. Existen ramplas "
"elípticas, verticais, horizontais e diagonais en &kappname;. Acerte coa bóla "
"no furado."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "Steepness"
msgstr "Inclinación"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The next tutorial hole has two slopes of differing steepness. If you "
#| "choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Info</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice>, the steepness of the slope will appear as a "
#| "number from 1-8, where 8 is steepest and 1 is shallowest. Hit the ball "
#| "into the hole and continue to the next hole."
msgid ""
"The next tutorial hole has two slopes of differing steepness. If you choose "
"the <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Info</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item, the steepness of the slope will appear "
"as a number from 1-8, where 8 is steepest and 1 is shallowest. Hit the ball "
"into the hole and continue to the next hole."
msgstr ""
"O próximo furado de tutorial ten dúas ramplas con inclinacións distintas. Se "
"escolles <menuchoice><guimenu>Furado</guimenu><guimenuitem>Mostrar "
"información</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, a inclinación da rampla aparece como "
"un número entre o 1 e o 8, en que o 8 é o máis inclinado e o 1 o máis chan. "
"Acerta no furado e pasa para o próximo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Walls"
msgstr "Paredes"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Balls bounce of walls as one would expect them to, with a little bit of "
"dampening. Deflect the ball off the walls and into the cup to advance to the "
"next hole."
msgstr ""
"As bólas rebotan nas paredes, como sería de esperar, cun lixeiro efecto. "
"Desvía a bóla das paredes para dentro da cova e avanza para o próximo furado."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:107 index.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid "Puddles and Sand"
msgstr "Pozas e area"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "Puddles"
msgstr "Pozas"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Puddles are blue. When your ball rolls into a puddle, a penalty stroke is "
"added to your score and you must then choose where you want to take your "
"next shot from: either next to the puddle or from the same place as where "
"you just took the last shot."
msgstr ""
"As pozas son azuis. Cando a bóla for parar a unha poza, engádese unha tacada "
"de penalización á puntuación e hai que escoller onde colocar a bóla: quere "
"preto da poza quere no mesmo sitio dese onde se fixo a última xogada."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sand"
msgstr "Area"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sand is yellow. Balls roll through sand very slowly."
msgstr "A area é amarela. As bólas rodan a través da area moi devagar."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hit the ball around the puddles and through the sand into the hole to "
"continue to the next tutorial hole."
msgstr ""
"Acerta na bóla arredor dos charcos e a través da area ata a meteres no "
"furado para continuar para o próximo furado do titorial."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:117 index.docbook:734
#, no-c-format
msgid "Windmills"
msgstr "Muíños"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Windmills are compound objects with brown border walls and a moving arm on "
"one side. Half-walls create the opening to the windmill, which the black arm "
"swings across. It takes practice to be able to time the stroke of the ball "
"to pass through the opening. Hit the ball through the windmill into the hole "
"to continue."
msgstr ""
"Os muíños son obxectos compostos con paredes de bordos castaños e cun brazo "
"móbel tanto na parte superior como na inferior do obxecto. As medias paredes "
"crean a abertura do muíño, arredor da cal roda un brazo preto. Esixe algunha "
"práctica para ser capaz de cronometrar a tacada da bóla para que pase pola "
"abertura. Acerte na bóla a través do muíño para o furado para poder "
"proseguir."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "Black Holes"
msgstr "Furados negros"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When you hit your ball into a black hole, it is transported to the exit "
#| "and ejected at the angle of the exit at a speed directly relational to "
#| "the speed your ball was going. Choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Info</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to see which "
#| "Black Hole goes to which exit and which direction the ball will come out "
#| "of the exit. The rim around Black Holes are the same color as their "
#| "corresponding exits. Hit the ball into the black hole, which will then "
#| "eject the ball into the cup so you can go to the next hole."
msgid ""
"When you hit your ball into a black hole, it is transported to the exit and "
"ejected at the angle of the exit at a speed directly relational to the speed "
"your ball was going. Choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Show Info</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item to see which "
"Black Hole goes to which exit and which direction the ball will come out of "
"the exit. The rim around Black Holes are the same color as their "
"corresponding exits. Hit the ball into the black hole, which will then eject "
"the ball into the cup so you can go to the next hole."
msgstr ""
"Cando se acerta coa bóla nun furado negro, esta é transportada para a saída "
"e expulsada co ángulo de saída a unha velocidade directamente proporcional á "
"velocidade con que a bóla ía. Escolle a opción <menuchoice><guimenu>Furado</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Mostrar informacións</guimenuitem></menuchoice> para "
"ver cal é o Furado Negro que vai a cada saída e con que dirección. O bordo "
"que hai arredor dos furados negros e das súas saídas correspondentes son da "
"mesma cor. Acerta coa bóla no furado negro, o cal expulsará entón a bóla "
"para o furado de maneira que se pase para o próximo nivel."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:125 index.docbook:749
#, no-c-format
msgid "Floaters"
msgstr "Boias"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Floaters are moving platforms that carry a ball that lands on it. Floaters' "
"speeds vary. This one is a pretty slow floater, but you still must time your "
"shot so you can go over the wall and into the cup."
msgstr ""
"As boias son plataformas móbiles que cargan unha bóla que pare encima delas. "
"A velocidade das boias pode variar. Esta é unha boia bastante lenta, pero "
"aínda así hai que cronometrar a tacada para que pase por riba da parede e "
"caia na cova."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bridges"
msgstr "Pontes"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Bridges are simple - they just lift the ball above the things below them, "
"like slopes, sand, and puddles. They can have brown walls on their perimeter."
msgstr ""
"As pontes son simples - simplemente elevan a bóla por riba das cousas que "
"haxa por baixo delas, como as ramplas, a area e as pozas. Poden ter paredes "
"castañas no seu perímetro."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Regras do xogo, estratexias e suxestións"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Here's in-depth description of &kappname;'s basic features."
msgid "Here's in-depth description of &kolf;'s basic features."
msgstr ""
"Velaquí unha descrición detallada das funcionalidades básicas de &kappname;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting a Game"
msgstr "Inicio dunha partida"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:141
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To start a game, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This opens a dialog "
#| "where you can configure your new game."
msgid ""
"To start a game, choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. This opens a dialog "
"where you can configure your new game."
msgstr ""
"Para comezar unha partida, escolle a opción <menuchoice><guimenu>Partida</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Nova</guimenuitem></menuchoice>.Ábrese un diálogo no "
"que se pode configurar a nova partida."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "Players Page"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a player to your game, click the <guibutton>New Player</guibutton> "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Para engadir un xogador á partida, preme o botón<guibutton>Novo xogador</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "To change the name of the players, change the text in the text boxes."
msgstr "Podes cambiar os nomes do equipo nas caixas de texto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove a player, click the <guibutton>Remove</guibutton> button next to "
"the player's name."
msgstr ""
"Para retirar un xogador, preme o botón <guibutton>Retirar</guibutton> que "
"hai ao lado do nome do xogador."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:167
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Course name:"
msgid "Course Page"
msgstr "Nome do campo:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To choose the course that you want to play, click its entry in the list "
#| "box on the left of this page. &kappname; comes with many built-in courses "
#| "that you can play."
msgid ""
"To choose the course that you want to play, click its entry in the list box "
"on the left of this page. &kolf; comes with many built-in courses that you "
"can play."
msgstr ""
"Para escoller o campo no que queres xogar, preme o seu nome na lista que hai "
"á esquerda desta páxina. &kappname; ven con varios campos incorporados nos "
"que se pode xogar."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To add a course that you have downloaded or made, click on the "
#| "<guibutton>Add...</guibutton> button on the bottom of this page, and "
#| "choose the course file in the file dialog."
msgid ""
"To add a course that you have downloaded or made, click on the "
"<guibutton>Add…</guibutton> button on the bottom of this page, and choose "
"the course file in the file dialog."
msgstr ""
"Para engadir un campo que descargases ou creases, preme o botón "
"<guibutton>Engadir…</guibutton> no fondo desta páxina e escolle o ficheiro "
"do campo no diálogo para escoller ficheiros."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options Page"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this page you can choose whether or not this game will be played in "
"<guilabel>Strict mode</guilabel>. In strict mode, there is no undo, moving "
"holes, or editing of the course. This mode is generally for competition. "
"Only in strict mode are high scores kept."
